&lt;p&gt;Senior IT Specialist (Citrix)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we’re looking for&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit a Citrix Senior IT Specialist into a varied and challenging post. We require highly motivated individuals who can contribute to project deliverables and operational service delivery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ideally, candidates must be educated to degree level or have equivalent experience within an IT infrastructure environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for an individuals who:-&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;manage, maintain and actively develop the national services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;work well alone and as part of a team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;take pride in service stability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;get satisfaction from fixing a complex issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;want to make a difference in the NHS in Wales.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;want to get involved with the latest technologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;want to implement new systems and services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;manage, maintain and actively develop the national services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;interested in job security tied to a good salary and pension bundle.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role will be focused on providing support for and implementing Citrix Technologies. Awareness of supporting infrastructure would be beneficial.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience of the following is essential:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Managing Citrix Virtual Apps &amp; Desktops (XenApp &amp; Xen Desktop)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Vendor Certification would be an advantage.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operating Systems&lt;/strong&gt;: Windows Server 2008 – 2019&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience of the following is desirable:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Citrix&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Citrix ADC (Load Balancing, Content Switching, GSLB)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Citrix Application Delivery Management (MAS)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Citrix Gateway&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Scripting &amp; Automation&lt;/strong&gt;: Powershell&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Networking&lt;/strong&gt;: Fundamentals of TCP/IP, networking interfaces and routing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Storage&lt;/strong&gt;: 3PAR San Storage Management, Storage Spaces Direct&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Virtualisation&lt;/strong&gt;: VmWare, Hyper V &amp; Citrix Hypervisor (XenServer)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security&lt;/strong&gt;: key security principles (Confidentiality, Integrity &amp; Availability)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for someone who will be responsible for the support and management of all aspects of provision of the specialist services for which the post holder is responsible.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Work with the Infrastructure Operations Technology Lead to deliver effective implementations and service stability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Manage and maintain the national services used to provide critical systems to NHS Wales.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is not a complete list of duties that will be required but covers the main aspects of the role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Training offered&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Industry seminars and in-house workshops.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- On-site technical training courses.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Vendor Training&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We have great benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We offer staff:-&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Automatic membership of the NHS pension scheme&lt;br /&gt;- 27 days paid leave plus bank holidays, increasing to 33 in two increments over ten years.&lt;br /&gt;- Childcare vouchers and flexible working hours&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like to contribute to the future of NHS Wales and make a contribution to the future of healthcare in Wales, then we would be delighted to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date: 1st December 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;David Owen&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Arweinydd Gweithrediadau Seilwaith (Gwasanaethau Ganolfan Ddata) | Infrastructure Operations Lead (Data Centre Services)&lt;br /&gt;Gwasanaeth Gwybodeg GIG Cymru | NHS Wales Informatics Service&lt;br /&gt;Tŷ Glan-yr-Afon, 21 Cowbridge Road East, Cardiff, CF11 9AD&lt;br /&gt;david.m.owen@wales.nhs.uk | 07891 421448&lt;/p&gt;
